  <data key="d4">"A land motor vehicle designed for use on public roads, which is the primary subject of the insurance policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"A land motor vehicle designed for use on public roads."&lt;SEP&gt;"A motor vehicle covered under the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"A single auto shown on the policy declarations has coverage limits applicable to it."&lt;SEP&gt;"A vehicle described in the policy, including a four-wheel private passenger auto or utility auto, where the sound system is installed."&lt;SEP&gt;"A vehicle owned by the policyholder or a resident relative but not insured under this coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"A vehicle that is considered separate from an attached trailer."&lt;SEP&gt;"An Auto is defined as a land motor vehicle designed for use on public roads."&lt;SEP&gt;"An auto described in the Policy Declarations is covered under the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"An auto is a vehicle covered under the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"An auto is a vehicle insured under the policy, and premiums are shown for each auto if more than one is insured."&lt;SEP&gt;"An auto is a vehicle involved in the incident that caused the injury."&lt;SEP&gt;"An auto is defined as a land motor vehicle designed for use on public roads, and is a key term in determining coverage and exclusions."&lt;SEP&gt;"An auto is defined as a land motor vehicle designed for use on public roads."&lt;SEP&gt;"An auto that must not be available or furnished for the regular use of an insured person."&lt;SEP&gt;"An auto used for the transportation of people or property for a fee is excluded."&lt;SEP&gt;"The auto is the vehicle being insured, which must be protected from further damage."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policy covers losses to the auto and related accidents or occurrences."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-442e0db5ed8682bcab7a54824da0d7b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ae46e2e200f1493ffb4202a0950ef80e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9177db9bf28d1b94e41d2945af46c2ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52f5f0f71f1ab344627208359e420446&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-edb30013271800ada18c87a8bc3e5cd1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a3c5316326203ee0a115e648929c62e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb067276caaf4fa58c030146cde3e6e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b55b5dbebd0735cd54f0def3352978c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de3dee890ed2c9f37d79ceb62462bb87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6e3ce49923cc6b8ff3ddc0cc91be876&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e112c7cb29439b72e7ec24cc60020e88&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ccb8c813f593e1d6b773fb60656c296b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-82005be4122ff546dea4915156b29767&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12ffe8b6b2ba410a0c8e955ca34e8cfb</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;NON-OWNED AUTO&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"OBJECT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A non-owned auto is a vehicle not owned by the insured but used with the owner's permission."&lt;SEP&gt;"A non-owned auto is a vehicle not owned by the policyholder but covered under the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"A non-owned auto is a vehicle not owned by the policyholder but used in auto business operations."&lt;SEP&gt;"A non-owned auto is a vehicle not owned by the policyholder or a resident, used with the owner's permission and not regularly available for use by the policyholder."&lt;SEP&gt;"A non-owned auto is covered for direct and accidental loss."&lt;SEP&gt;"A non-owned auto is covered for loss not caused by collision."&lt;SEP&gt;"A non-owned auto is not owned by the insured, and coverage applies only after all other collectible auto medical insurance is exhausted."&lt;SEP&gt;"A non-owned auto with at least four wheels is covered if used with permission."&lt;SEP&gt;"A vehicle not owned by the insured but covered under the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"A vehicle not owned by the policyholder or a resident, used in a business or occupation, which may trigger exclusion under U M 2."&lt;SEP&gt;"A vehicle not owned by the policyholder or a resident, used with the owner's permission, and not regularly available for the use of an insured person. It is covered under the policy under specific conditions."&lt;SEP&gt;"A vehicle not owned by the policyholder or resident relative."&lt;SEP&gt;"An auto not owned by the insured person but used by them."&lt;SEP&gt;"An automobile not owned by the policyholder but used by them, which is covered under the policy."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-442e0db5ed8682bcab7a54824da0d7b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a3c5316326203ee0a115e648929c62e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a1058b402f07e43095cfbfe1691d379&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb067276caaf4fa58c030146cde3e6e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b55b5dbebd0735cd54f0def3352978c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6215ed56b5c8c7128976e54f6afde15b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8be2695f13a2055df9eb3b1f448e01ac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e112c7cb29439b72e7ec24cc60020e88&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ccb8c813f593e1d6b773fb60656c296b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-82005be4122ff546dea4915156b29767&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12ffe8b6b2ba410a0c8e955ca34e8cfb</data>
