  <data key="d4">"A loss between $50 and $100 is partially covered."&lt;SEP&gt;"A loss covered by other insurance, affecting Allstate’s payment."&lt;SEP&gt;"A loss is subject to appraisal by either party."&lt;SEP&gt;"A loss of $100 or more is covered."&lt;SEP&gt;"A loss that can be subject to appraisal by either the insured or Allstate."&lt;SEP&gt;"A loss that may be compensated through money, repair, or replacement."&lt;SEP&gt;"A loss that may be settled with the insured or the property owner."&lt;SEP&gt;"Loss caused intentionally by or at the direction of an insured person is not covered."&lt;SEP&gt;"Loss to a permanently installed sound system is covered."&lt;SEP&gt;"No payment is made if the loss is $50 or less."&lt;SEP&gt;"The loss must meet certain conditions for the deductible to be waived."</data>
