<node id="&quot;YOU&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d4">"'You' refers to the policyholder named on the Policy Declarations and that policyholder's resident spouse."&lt;SEP&gt;"An individual who has the right to demand an appraisal of the loss."&lt;SEP&gt;"The insured individual who may be involved in settling a claim."&lt;SEP&gt;"The insured person named on the Policy Declarations."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder is a party to the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder is an insured person under the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder named on the Policy Declarations, including their resident spouse, who are the primary insured parties."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder named on the Policy Declarations."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder pays the difference between the loss and $100."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder, who is an insured person."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder, who is exempt from the exclusion when injured as a co-worker."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder, who may be covered for bodily injury to themselves or household residents related by blood, marriage, or adoption."&lt;SEP&gt;"You are an insured person who may be covered under the policy, including relatives living in your household."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9464bb7af811d8f15562644a4b28627a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de9df743c1a11a8ab7dd8d3778fbd139&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a3c5316326203ee0a115e648929c62e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-810b812ea27a9a4ae98ffeee6a14930d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a1058b402f07e43095cfbfe1691d379&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b55b5dbebd0735cd54f0def3352978c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb067276caaf4fa58c030146cde3e6e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6215ed56b5c8c7128976e54f6afde15b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ccb8c813f593e1d6b773fb60656c296b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12ffe8b6b2ba410a0c8e955ca34e8cfb</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;REVOLUTION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A fundamental change in political power or organizational structures."&lt;SEP&gt;"A revolution is an exclusion from disability coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"Revolution is an event that excludes coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"Revolution is an event that results in damage or loss not covered."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-de3dee890ed2c9f37d79ceb62462bb87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ccb8c813f593e1d6b773fb60656c296b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52f5f0f71f1ab344627208359e420446&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b55b5dbebd0735cd54f0def3352978c</data>
