</node>
<node id="&quot;AUTO ACCIDENT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A single incident involving a vehicle that may result in expenses for the insured person."&lt;SEP&gt;"An auto accident is an incident involving a vehicle that causes injury or illness."&lt;SEP&gt;"An auto accident is an incident involving a vehicle that may lead to legal action and requires immediate notification."&lt;SEP&gt;"An auto accident is the cause of bodily injury, sickness, disease, or death that triggers coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"An auto accident is the event that must cause the injury, sickness, or disease."&lt;SEP&gt;"An incident involving a motor vehicle that may lead to claims."&lt;SEP&gt;"An incident involving a vehicle that results in damage or injury."&lt;SEP&gt;"An incident involving the insured auto that results in injury or damage."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-442e0db5ed8682bcab7a54824da0d7b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b1a9c0ee5abff30de9434ff54575a1d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52f5f0f71f1ab344627208359e420446&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a3c5316326203ee0a115e648929c62e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6215ed56b5c8c7128976e54f6afde15b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e112c7cb29439b72e7ec24cc60020e88&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ccb8c813f593e1d6b773fb60656c296b</data>
</node>
