  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PROCESS"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A process to determine the value of a loss, which both the insured and Allstate can demand."&lt;SEP&gt;"Appraisal is a process to determine the value of a loss."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-7b55b5dbebd0735cd54f0def3352978c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12ffe8b6b2ba410a0c8e955ca34e8cfb</data>
</node>
