<node id="&quot;SOUND SYSTEM&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"OBJECT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A Sound System is any device within the insured auto designed for voice or video transmission, voice, video, or radar signal reception, recording or playing back recorded material, or supplying power to cellular or similar telephone equipment."&lt;SEP&gt;"A sound system is any device within the insured auto designed for voice or video transmission, or for voice, video, or radar signal reception."&lt;SEP&gt;"A sound system permanently installed in an auto using bolts, brackets, or other means, and its associated antennas or apparatus used specifically with the system."&lt;SEP&gt;"A sound system permanently installed in the auto by bolts, brackets, or other means is covered."&lt;SEP&gt;"Loss to any sound system within the auto is excluded."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-8be2695f13a2055df9eb3b1f448e01ac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9177db9bf28d1b94e41d2945af46c2ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-82005be4122ff546dea4915156b29767&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b55b5dbebd0735cd54f0def3352978c</data>
