<node id="&quot;BENEFIT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The benefit is a financial payment made upon the death of an insured person."&lt;SEP&gt;"The benefit is the amount paid by Allstate as shown on the Policy Declarations."&lt;SEP&gt;"The insurer has a financial interest in the recovery of damages, and thus the rights must be preserved for their benefit."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-442e0db5ed8682bcab7a54824da0d7b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-73e94c444615403bb65cb8316d74e2ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52f5f0f71f1ab344627208359e420446</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;POLICY PERIOD&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"TIME PERIOD"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The policy applies only during the specified policy period, which is shown on the Policy Declarations."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policy period is the duration during which the insurance policy is active."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policy period is the time frame during which the insurance policy is active."&lt;SEP&gt;"The time frame during which the insurance policy is active and in effect, during which the policyholder may acquire new vehicles that qualify for coverage under the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"The time frame during which the insurance policy is active."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9464bb7af811d8f15562644a4b28627a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb067276caaf4fa58c030146cde3e6e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6215ed56b5c8c7128976e54f6afde15b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ae46e2e200f1493ffb4202a0950ef80e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-82005be4122ff546dea4915156b29767</data>
</node>
