  <data key="d2">chunk-b6e3ce49923cc6b8ff3ddc0cc91be876</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;RESIDENT RELATIVE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A person who resides in the policyholder's household and is related by blood, marriage, or adoption, and is permitted to use a non-owned auto with the owner's consent."&lt;SEP&gt;"A relative of the policyholder who lives in the same household and uses a four-wheel private passenger or utility auto."&lt;SEP&gt;"A relative of the policyholder who resides in the household."&lt;SEP&gt;"A relative who lives with the policyholder and owns property in the insured auto."&lt;SEP&gt;"A resident relative is a person who lives in the household and is related to the policyholder."&lt;SEP&gt;"A resident relative is covered when operating or occupying a non-owned vehicle."&lt;SEP&gt;"A resident relative is someone living in the same household and covered under the policy."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9177db9bf28d1b94e41d2945af46c2ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a3c5316326203ee0a115e648929c62e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb067276caaf4fa58c030146cde3e6e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6215ed56b5c8c7128976e54f6afde15b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ccb8c813f593e1d6b773fb60656c296b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-82005be4122ff546dea4915156b29767</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BODILY INJURY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Bodily injury caused by an auto accident is a condition that may lead to benefit payment."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bodily injury is a physical harm caused by an auto accident and qualifies for coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bodily injury is a physical harm caused by an auto accident."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bodily injury is physical harm caused by a hit-and-run vehicle."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bodily injury refers to physical harm or injury sustained by individuals in a motor vehicle accident."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bodily injury refers to physical harm suffered by a person due to an accident."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bodily injury refers to physical harm suffered by the insured person, which may give rise to a right to recover damages."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bodily injury refers to physical harm suffered by the policyholder, a relative, or an occupant of an insured auto."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bodily injury refers to physical harm sustained by a person, which may lead to legal liability."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physical harm or injury to a person, including sickness, disease, or death."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physical harm suffered by an insured person, which must be caused by an accident and arise from the use of an uninsured auto."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physical harm to a person, excluded from coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physical harm to a person."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physical harm, sickness, disease, or death sustained by a person."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physical injury, sickness, disease, or death resulting from an accident, which may be covered or excluded based on policy terms."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physical injury, sickness, disease, or death resulting from an accident, which may be excluded under E 3."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physical injury, sickness, disease, or death resulting from an accident, which may be subject to exclusion under certain conditions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physical injury, sickness, disease, or death, which is a covered or excluded event depending on policy terms."&lt;SEP&gt;"The bodily injury must have continuously prevented the insured person from performing all duties."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9464bb7af811d8f15562644a4b28627a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-442e0db5ed8682bcab7a54824da0d7b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6e59deb97f8984555fae3eed52c917fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52f5f0f71f1ab344627208359e420446&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a3c5316326203ee0a115e648929c62e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-810b812ea27a9a4ae98ffeee6a14930d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb067276caaf4fa58c030146cde3e6e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6215ed56b5c8c7128976e54f6afde15b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-73e94c444615403bb65cb8316d74e2ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de3dee890ed2c9f37d79ceb62462bb87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6e3ce49923cc6b8ff3ddc0cc91be876&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ccb8c813f593e1d6b773fb60656c296b</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ADDITIONAL PREMIUM&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"FINANCIAL OBLIGATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"An additional premium is required when adding a new auto to the policy, paid to extend coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"An additional premium must be paid for coverage of a newly acquired auto."&lt;SEP&gt;"An additional premium must be paid when acquiring a new motor vehicle during the policy period."&lt;SEP&gt;"The extra cost incurred by the policyholder when adding a new vehicle to the policy, required to be paid after acquiring a new auto during the policy period."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9464bb7af811d8f15562644a4b28627a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a3c5316326203ee0a115e648929c62e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb067276caaf4fa58c030146cde3e6e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-82005be4122ff546dea4915156b29767</data>
</node>
