  <data key="d3">"SECTION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A section outlining the insured’s obligation to assist the insurer during claims."&lt;SEP&gt;"Assistance and cooperation require the insured to provide necessary information and support to the insurer during claim processing."</data>
