  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The consent granted by the owner of a non-owned auto allowing the policyholder or a resident relative to use the vehicle."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder must have the owner's permission to operate a motor vehicle not owned by them."&lt;SEP&gt;"The temporary use of a motor vehicle must be with the owner's permission."&lt;SEP&gt;"The use of a non-owned auto must be with the owner's permission to be covered."&lt;SEP&gt;"The use of non-owned autos must be with the owner's permission to be covered."&lt;SEP&gt;"Use of a non-owned auto requires permission from the owner."</data>
