<node id="&quot;TRAVEL-TRAILER&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"OBJECT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A Travel-trailer is a trailer of the house, cabin, or camping type that is equipped or used as a living quarters."&lt;SEP&gt;"A travel-trailer is a vehicle that may be rented, but loss is excluded unless a specific premium is shown."&lt;SEP&gt;"A travel-trailer is a vehicle that may contain appliances, furniture, equipment, and accessories."&lt;SEP&gt;"A travel-trailer is not covered unless described on the Policy Declarations."&lt;SEP&gt;"A travel-trailer that may not be rented to anyone else unless a specific premium is shown on the Policy Declarations."&lt;SEP&gt;"A type of vehicle that is excluded from this coverage provision."&lt;SEP&gt;"A vehicle type excluded from transportation reimbursement provision."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9177db9bf28d1b94e41d2945af46c2ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-82005be4122ff546dea4915156b29767&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b55b5dbebd0735cd54f0def3352978c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12ffe8b6b2ba410a0c8e955ca34e8cfb</data>
