<node id="&quot;PRIVATE PASSENGER AUTO&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"OBJECT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A land motor vehicle designed for personal use on public roads, which is exempt from the U M 2 exclusion when used by the policyholder, chauffeur, or domestic servant."&lt;SEP&gt;"A land motor vehicle designed for use on public roads, used for personal transportation, and not for commercial purposes. It is eligible to tow a trailer under the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"A private passenger auto is a vehicle designed for personal use on public roads."&lt;SEP&gt;"A private passenger auto is a vehicle designed for transporting people and not for commercial use."&lt;SEP&gt;"A private passenger auto is a vehicle designed for transporting people."&lt;SEP&gt;"A type of auto designed for personal use, used in conjunction with a trailer."&lt;SEP&gt;"A vehicle designed for personal use, used by the policyholder, chauffeur, or servant."&lt;SEP&gt;"A vehicle used for personal transportation, covered under the policy."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-1a3c5316326203ee0a115e648929c62e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb067276caaf4fa58c030146cde3e6e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6215ed56b5c8c7128976e54f6afde15b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ccb8c813f593e1d6b773fb60656c296b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-82005be4122ff546dea4915156b29767</data>
