  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"An event where the auto is damaged due to impact with another object, requiring collision insurance for coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"Collision is a peril that is covered, except when the loss is caused by collision."&lt;SEP&gt;"Collision of a conveyance during transport is a covered peril."&lt;SEP&gt;"Collision with another object or upset of the auto or trailer is covered."&lt;SEP&gt;"Loss not caused by collision is covered."</data>
