<node id="&quot;EARTHQUAKE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A natural disaster that can cause physical damage to the auto and its contents."&lt;SEP&gt;"Loss caused by earthquake is covered."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9177db9bf28d1b94e41d2945af46c2ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a1058b402f07e43095cfbfe1691d379</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;STRUCK AS A PEDESTRIAN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Being struck as a pedestrian by a vehicle is a condition for disability coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"Being struck as a pedestrian by a vehicle is an excluded event."&lt;SEP&gt;"Being struck as a pedestrian is a scenario under which disability may be excluded."&lt;SEP&gt;"The injury must occur when the insured person is struck as a pedestrian by an auto, trailer, or semi-trailer."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-442e0db5ed8682bcab7a54824da0d7b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de3dee890ed2c9f37d79ceb62462bb87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52f5f0f71f1ab344627208359e420446</data>
</node>
