  <data key="d2">chunk-b6e3ce49923cc6b8ff3ddc0cc91be876</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;EXPLOSION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"An event involving sudden release of energy that can damage the auto and its contents."&lt;SEP&gt;"Loss caused by explosion is covered."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9177db9bf28d1b94e41d2945af46c2ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a1058b402f07e43095cfbfe1691d379</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;TRAILER&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"OBJECT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A trailer attached to a private passenger auto or utility auto, which is exempt from the U M 2 exclusion when used by the policyholder, chauffeur, or domestic servant."&lt;SEP&gt;"A trailer attached to an insured auto, designed for use with a private passenger auto or utility auto, and cannot be used for business purposes except with a private passenger auto or utility auto."&lt;SEP&gt;"A trailer is a vehicle attached to an auto and covered under the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"A trailer is a vehicle attached to an insured auto, designed for use with a private passenger auto, and not used for business purposes unless specified."&lt;SEP&gt;"A trailer is a vehicle that can be attached to a motor vehicle and is involved in the incident."&lt;SEP&gt;"A trailer is covered when attached to an insured auto."&lt;SEP&gt;"A trailer that is attached to an insured auto and designed for use with a private passenger auto or utility auto. It is covered under the policy only if it is not used for business purposes, except when used with a private passenger auto or utility auto."&lt;SEP&gt;"A vehicle attached to a private passenger auto, used in other business or occupations."&lt;SEP&gt;"A vehicle towed by a motor vehicle, used for transporting goods or equipment."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-442e0db5ed8682bcab7a54824da0d7b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52f5f0f71f1ab344627208359e420446&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a3c5316326203ee0a115e648929c62e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb067276caaf4fa58c030146cde3e6e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ccb8c813f593e1d6b773fb60656c296b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-82005be4122ff546dea4915156b29767</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CAMPER UNIT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"OBJECT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A camper unit is a demountable living unit designed for temporary residence, including built-in equipment and accessories."&lt;SEP&gt;"A camper unit is a unit that may be mounted or not, and is excluded unless described on the Policy Declarations."&lt;SEP&gt;"A camper unit is not covered unless described on the Policy Declarations."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-82005be4122ff546dea4915156b29767&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b55b5dbebd0735cd54f0def3352978c</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;COVERED TRAILER&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
