<node id="&quot;UTILITY AUTO&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"OBJECT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A Utility Auto is a vehicle of the pick-up body, sedan delivery, or panel truck type with a rated load capacity of not more than 2,000 pounds."&lt;SEP&gt;"A land motor vehicle of the pick-up body, sedan delivery, or panel truck type with a rated load capacity of not more than 2,000 pounds. It is eligible to tow a trailer under the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"A land motor vehicle of the pick-up body, sedan delivery, or panel truck type, with a rated load capacity of 2,000 pounds or less, used for personal or non-commercial purposes."&lt;SEP&gt;"A type of auto covered under the policy, including replacement vehicles."&lt;SEP&gt;"A type of auto including pickup body, sedan delivery, or panel truck, with a rated load capacity of not more than 2,000 pounds."&lt;SEP&gt;"A type of auto, such as a pickup, sedan delivery, or panel truck, with a rated load capacity of not more than 2,000 pounds, used in conjunction with a trailer."&lt;SEP&gt;"A utility auto is a land motor vehicle of the pick-up body, sedan delivery, or panel truck type with a rated load capacity of not more than 2,000 pounds. It is covered under the policy if all other private passenger autos or utility autos owned by the policyholder are insured, provided the policyholder notifies Allstate within 60 days of acquisition and pays any additional premium."&lt;SEP&gt;"A utility auto is a vehicle designed for practical use, such as delivery or work, covered under the policy if described in the declarations or replaced within 60 days."&lt;SEP&gt;"A utility auto is a vehicle used for practical purposes and covered under the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"A utility auto is a vehicle used for practical purposes."&lt;SEP&gt;"A vehicle used for practical purposes, such as delivery or transport, covered under the policy."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9177db9bf28d1b94e41d2945af46c2ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a3c5316326203ee0a115e648929c62e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb067276caaf4fa58c030146cde3e6e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b55b5dbebd0735cd54f0def3352978c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6215ed56b5c8c7128976e54f6afde15b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ccb8c813f593e1d6b773fb60656c296b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-82005be4122ff546dea4915156b29767</data>
</node>
