  <data key="d3">"LOCATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A group of people living together in a residence."&lt;SEP&gt;"A group of people living together in a single residence, including the policyholder and their dependents."&lt;SEP&gt;"A household is a group of people living together in a residence."&lt;SEP&gt;"A household is a group of people living together, and the spouse must reside in the same household as the insured."&lt;SEP&gt;"A household is a living arrangement where relatives reside with the policyholder."&lt;SEP&gt;"Residents may intend to resume residing in a household."&lt;SEP&gt;"The household includes drivers whose information affects the policy."</data>
