<node id="&quot;POLICY DECLARATIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"DOCUMENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">The Policy Declarations are a critical section of an insurance policy that serve as an official document outlining the core terms, coverage, and key details of the policy. This document includes the names of the insured parties, the policyholder, and the insurance company referred to as "We," "Us," or "Allstate." It specifies the vehicles covered under the policy, including details on each insured auto, and may also describe additional assets such as a camper unit. The Policy Declarations list all insured autos and their applicable coverage limits, including specific coverages such as Coverage ZA, Coverage ZZ, Coverage CW, and Coverage CM, with clear indication of which coverages apply as noted on the document. It details the total liability limit for each loss under Coverage ZZ and the limit of liability for various coverages, including the total limit of liability for each loss. The document also specifies the deductible for each coverage, the premium details for rented vehicles, and the weekly benefit amount where applicable. Additionally, it includes the policy period, the insurance amount, and the benefit amount, all of which constitute essential policy details. The Policy Declarations are a foundational component of the policy, containing key information such as coverage limits, insured parties, vehicles, and premium details, and must be countersigned by an authorized agent to be valid. Overall, the Policy Declarations function as a comprehensive summary of the policy’s essential elements, ensuring clarity on coverage, limits, and responsibilities.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9464bb7af811d8f15562644a4b28627a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b55b5dbebd0735cd54f0def3352978c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6e3ce49923cc6b8ff3ddc0cc91be876&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8be2695f13a2055df9eb3b1f448e01ac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ae46e2e200f1493ffb4202a0950ef80e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-82005be4122ff546dea4915156b29767&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12ffe8b6b2ba410a0c8e955ca34e8cfb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52f5f0f71f1ab344627208359e420446&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de9df743c1a11a8ab7dd8d3778fbd139&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-442e0db5ed8682bcab7a54824da0d7b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6e59deb97f8984555fae3eed52c917fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb067276caaf4fa58c030146cde3e6e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6215ed56b5c8c7128976e54f6afde15b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de3dee890ed2c9f37d79ceb62462bb87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9177db9bf28d1b94e41d2945af46c2ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b1a9c0ee5abff30de9434ff54575a1d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-edb30013271800ada18c87a8bc3e5cd1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a3c5316326203ee0a115e648929c62e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-810b812ea27a9a4ae98ffeee6a14930d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a1058b402f07e43095cfbfe1691d379&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ccb8c813f593e1d6b773fb60656c296b</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;INSURED PERSON&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d4">The INSURED PERSON is an individual covered under the auto insurance policy, including the person named on the policy as the covered party, relatives, occupants of insured vehicles, and those legally entitled to recover benefits. This person may be legally obligated to pay damages or may be legally entitled to damages, and is protected by the policy from liability for damages related to an insured auto. The INSURED PERSON is covered under the policy when occupying a vehicle during an accident, and their use of the auto may trigger coverage. They may receive benefits such as payment for medical expenses, funeral service expenses in the event of death due to a covered auto accident, or compensation for disability, with eligibility determined by the policy terms, including the individual’s ability to perform occupational duties. The INSURED PERSON has a right to benefits, and the amount payable is determined either by agreement with Allstate or, if no agreement is reached, by arbitration. The individual must cooperate with the insurer in the defense of any claim or lawsuit, must be informed immediately if sued, and must notify Allstate in a timely manner if initiating legal action against a party believed responsible for an accident—failure to do so may result in loss of protection under any resulting judgment. The INSURED PERSON may be required to undergo medical examinations by physicians chosen by the insurer, and must be alive for benefits to be paid. Additionally, the insured person is responsible for paying the arbitrator they select. The INSURED PERSON is an individual protected by the policy, whose actions and circumstances are central to determining benefit eligibility and coverage.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9464bb7af811d8f15562644a4b28627a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-442e0db5ed8682bcab7a54824da0d7b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6e59deb97f8984555fae3eed52c917fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52f5f0f71f1ab344627208359e420446&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b1a9c0ee5abff30de9434ff54575a1d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a3c5316326203ee0a115e648929c62e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-810b812ea27a9a4ae98ffeee6a14930d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a1058b402f07e43095cfbfe1691d379&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b55b5dbebd0735cd54f0def3352978c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb067276caaf4fa58c030146cde3e6e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6215ed56b5c8c7128976e54f6afde15b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-73e94c444615403bb65cb8316d74e2ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de3dee890ed2c9f37d79ceb62462bb87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e112c7cb29439b72e7ec24cc60020e88&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6e3ce49923cc6b8ff3ddc0cc91be876&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ccb8c813f593e1d6b773fb60656c296b</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ALLSTATE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">Allstate, referring to the Allstate Insurance Company or Allstate Indemnity Company as specified in the Policy Declarations, is an insurance organization that issues and signs insurance policies, enters into legal contracts with policyholders, and provides coverage for various risks, including auto, property, and medical expenses. As the insurer responsible for administering the policy, Allstate is the entity that pays benefits as specified in the policy, including weekly benefits, direct and accidental losses not caused by collision, and losses caused by perils listed under Coverage HE or HF. Allstate pays for damages to insured or non-owned autos, general average and salvage charges when an insured auto is being transported, and may pay for a loss in money, repair, or replacement of damaged or stolen property. The insurer’s liability is limited to the actual cash value of the property, and it pays only after all other collectible insurance has been exhausted.

Allstate has the right to adjust premiums based on updated or inaccurate information provided by the policyholder, and it uses information from the policyholder or other sources to determine premium amounts. The company requires cooperation from the policyholder to verify information and may broaden coverage without additional charge. Allstate must insure all other private passenger motor vehicles owned by the policyholder if an additional vehicle is to be covered. It also has the right to appraisal, the right to conduct an autopsy, and the right to recover from third parties upon payment of a claim.

Allstate is a party to the agreement and negotiates benefits and amounts payable with insured persons; if no agreement is reached, it may use arbitration to decide. The insurer may cancel the policy after 60 days and is not bound by any judgment if an insured person sues without providing adequate notice for intervention. Allstate is the insurance company that may pay damages and is the entity responsible for managing claims, ensuring compliance with policy terms, and fulfilling its obligations under the policy.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9464bb7af811d8f15562644a4b28627a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-442e0db5ed8682bcab7a54824da0d7b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ae46e2e200f1493ffb4202a0950ef80e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52f5f0f71f1ab344627208359e420446&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-edb30013271800ada18c87a8bc3e5cd1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a3c5316326203ee0a115e648929c62e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-810b812ea27a9a4ae98ffeee6a14930d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a1058b402f07e43095cfbfe1691d379&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b55b5dbebd0735cd54f0def3352978c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb067276caaf4fa58c030146cde3e6e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de3dee890ed2c9f37d79ceb62462bb87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8be2695f13a2055df9eb3b1f448e01ac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e112c7cb29439b72e7ec24cc60020e88&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6e3ce49923cc6b8ff3ddc0cc91be876&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ccb8c813f593e1d6b773fb60656c296b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-82005be4122ff546dea4915156b29767&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12ffe8b6b2ba410a0c8e955ca34e8cfb</data>
